{"tid":1640093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［支持義士們請入嚟］希望大家唔好對天琦咁高期望同俾壓力佢","createTime":"2019-10-09T00:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T11:42:38.000Z","uid":28818,"like":580,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"f95c6c5b14989b58f9cd8b32e75f9dedd363a6d8","tid":1640093,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:11:31.000Z","msg":"引用黃台仰嘅一句說話<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「沒有任何一個人的責任是為你犧牲的」</span><br />\n<br />\n見到大家晨咁早去高院排隊，一個月前已經倒數，明白大家都好想天梁天琦可以減刑盡早出獄，我都係。<br />\n但無論上訴結果點，我哋都需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">繼續抗爭</span>。<br />\n天琦係精神領袖，係點醒我哋嘅人，就連光復香港時代革命都係佢提出嘅。<br />\n同時佢為香港已經犧牲咗好多，就算佢出獄之後想繼續抗爭，定係想繼續讀書，決定不理世事，我哋都要支持，唔好俾壓力同說話佢聽。<br />\n<br />\n琴日見到有人開post討論「如果天琦出返嚟佢會擔任咩位置？」，大家點解assume咗佢一番出嚟就會繼續抗爭呢？我覺得大家可以思考下。<br />\n<br />\n就算佢繼續出嚟做大家嘅軍師，大家都要俾時間佢適應依家嘅環境，吸收資訊。佢想/佢適合擔任咩位置都好，<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔急，慢慢嚟，唔好唔記得今次係長期抗爭</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，除咗天琦之外，仲有兩位義士。包括<span style=\"color: red;\">判3年6個月嘅黃家駒義士，同判得最重，7年嘅盧建民義士。</span>7月頭嘅時候，幾位義士死諫，盧義士同我地講<span style=\"color: gold;\">「無論政權有多不堪，不濟，各位千萬千萬不要放棄生命。 各位要留有有用之軀，一起抵抗共產政權的吞佔。沒有人是一座孤島，可以自全，每個人都是大陸的一部份，無論誰死，誰受傷，都是我的一部份漸漸逝去和損毀。光明會驅逐黑暗！」</span>（quote咗大部分）<span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家係關心天琦嘅同時，都要關心埋其他義士。</span><br />\n<br />\n如果有義士家屬攞唔到飛入去旁聽，而你又有飛嘅話希望你可以交俾家屬，我諗佢哋最需要嘅都係家屬嘅支持。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaL9jbz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaL9jbz.jpg&h=7887e677&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b74a33c7ab23cbc282b353c7fe182f1e9cabeaae","tid":1640093,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e5f946a505a47c10346a5e303705bbef460fba","tid":1640093,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d4e3af7e3f5533905a7997ae49cb1bf6bee12e","tid":1640093,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:13:28.000Z","msg":"係咪太早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f34a74455acf22eba9fb3c1f68b62d45a1f6c5","tid":1640093,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:13:55.000Z","msg":"喂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f95f77b951ff44f066dea16bf78e07be442051","tid":1640093,"uid":28818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:14:26.000Z","msg":"人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622baf650bd4d544d79860e1963ff7d3921667a4","tid":1640093,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:14:58.000Z","msg":"去高院小心大頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640029</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"59b53332aa1ce9ab5f1675824e883ed9afd8f424","tid":1640093,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:15:40.000Z","msg":"[香港本土書店List]裝飾罷買三中商，中共思想控制香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632803</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e81f1e7fde9a7256a30fef8295c877812b4f287","tid":1640093,"uid":258718,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:16:11.000Z","msg":"其實雨革 魚革入左去既又邊止得呢幾個<br />\n關心下其他人好嗎"},{"pid":"d3f33dd813668d6c3bdf1393d596d9849d5d15b4","tid":1640093,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:16:13.000Z","msg":"正評咗嘅巴絲 幫手推好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea718b6ceffda63824be130ab617f75e1e74808","tid":1640093,"uid":258091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB